com.foreach.across.modules.spring.security.acl.ui

Class AclPermissionsFormSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.spring.security.acl.ui.AclPermissionsFormSection

  • public class AclPermissionsFormSection
extends Object
    Represents a single section of an ACL permissions form for an entity. Requires a unique name and a AclPermissionsFormPermissionGroup supplier.

    Allows for full customization of every element of a section, but most can be left empty and will get default values when executed by the AclPermissionsFormViewProcessor.

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    AclPermissionsForm, AclPermissionsFormPermissionGroup
